							<div style="margin-left: 8%; margin-right: 8%;" class="section-title">
								<h4 style="text-align: center">What is GojoRent?</h4>
								<p>GojoRent is a web application that aims to streamline the process of finding and
									renting a home. By eliminating brokers from the equation, GojoRent allows renters to
									directly connect with house owners and search for available properties in their
									area. The application is built with a combination of front-end technologies such as
									HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, and a backend framework written in Node.js and Express.
								</p><br>

								<h4 style="text-align: center">How it Works</h4>
								<p>Renters can easily search for available homes on GojoRent by specifying their desired
									location, budget, and other relevant criteria. The application then returns a list
									of homes that match the search criteria, complete with photos, descriptions, and
									contact information for the house owner. Renters can directly contact the house
									owner to inquire about the property or schedule a viewing.

								On the other hand, house owners can use GojoRent to advertise their available homes for
								rent. They can create a listing with photos, descriptions, and other relevant details,
								and make it visible to renters searching for homes in the area. By using GojoRent, house
								owners can reach a wider audience of potential renters and save time and money on broker
								fees.</p><br>

								<h4 style="text-align: center">Benefits for Renters</h4>
								<p>GojoRent provides several benefits for renters. By eliminating brokers from the
									equation, renters can directly interact with house owners and negotiate rental terms
									without intermediaries. This can lead to more favorable rental agreements and reduce
									the risk of misunderstandings or disputes. In addition, GojoRent allows renters to
									search for available homes in their desired location and budget, making it easier to
									find a home that meets their needs and preferences.</p><br>

								<h4 style="text-align: center">Benefits for House Owners</h4>
								<p>GojoRent also offers several benefits for house owners. By advertising their
									available homes on the platform, house owners can reach a wider audience of
									potential renters and save money on broker fees. In addition, GojoRent allows house
									owners to directly interact with renters, making it easier to screen potential
									tenants and negotiate rental terms. By using GojoRent, house owners can streamline
									the process of renting out their homes and save time and resources in the process.
								</p><br>

								<h4 style="text-align: center">Conclusion</h4>
								<p>GojoRent is a simple and effective web application that makes it easier for renters
									to find homes and for house owners to advertise their available properties. By
									eliminating brokers from the equation, GojoRent allows renters and house owners to
									directly interact and negotiate rental terms, leading to more favorable agreements
									and a better experience for all parties involved.</p>
